lead_paragraph: Scott McCarron eagled the par-5 12th and shot a 5-under 66 on Saturday to take a two-stroke lead in the Pacific Links Bear Mountain Championship.

headline.print_headline: Scott McCarron Takes 2-Shot Lead in PGA Tour Champions Event
